gcdFunction = (a, b, x, y) ->
    if a is 0
        x = 0
        y = 1
        return b

    x1 = 0
    y1 = 0
    gcd = gcdFunction b % a, a, x1, y1

    x = y1 - Math.floor (b / a) * x1
    y = x1

    gcd
